Hand Painted Antique Bronze and Metallic Finish
A Great Gift For Bee Lovers and Steampunk Enthusiasts
description: Make a bold statement in your home, office, or library with this steampunk-inspired Steambee bookend from artist Brigid Ashwood! This 7.5-inch tall, 4.5-inch long, 4.5-inch wide (19x11x11 cm) bookend is expertly cast in resin and hand-painted in an antique bronze and metallic finish with lightly colored accents enhancing all the amazing detail; from the bee's wings to the mechanical gears and cogs. Elegant lines and elements of nature come together in this beautiful blending of bug and machine, and it's great as a gift any steampunk enthusiast is sure to admire!
